02008.%20Located%20downtown%2C%20it's%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20stay%20if%20you%20want%20to%20walk%20to%20the%20waterfront%20or%20Pike%20Place%20Market%20in%20five%20minutes%20or%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hotel%20has%20won%20many%20awards%2C%20including%20being%20named%20the%20No.%201%20hotel%20in%20Washington%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.fourseasons.com%2Fseattle%2Fhotel-news%2F2024%2Fbest-hotel-in-seattle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20News%20%26amp%3B%20World%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024.%20A%20hotel%20rep%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20Seattle%20has%20hosted%20some%20celebrity%20guests%2C%20though%20he%20didn't%20specify%20who.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIf%20you%20stay%20in%20a%20corner%20room%20like%20I%20did%2C%20you'll%20have%20constant%20views%20of%20the%20bay%20and%20downtown%20Seattle.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221919%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20a%20Four%20Seasons%20room%20with%20a%20table%20and%20chairs%20in%20front%20of%20florr-to-ceiling%20windows%20showing%20the%20bay%20outside%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687933cbf748d8c055f5d067%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20Seasons%20Seattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stayed%20in%20a%20Corner%20Deluxe%20Bay%20View%20King%20room%20with%20a%20starting%20rate%20of%20%24965%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-know-before-visiting-italy-tourist-season-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epeak%20season%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20May%20to%20September%2C%20and%20during%20the%20end-of-year%20holidays.%20BI%20received%20a%20media%20rate%20for%20the%20one-night%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20lobby%20was%20modern%20and%20classy%2C%20with%20natural%20hues%20and%20pops%20of%20pink.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20the%20lobby%20at%2