C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20enter%20the%20mudroom%2C%20the%20long-awaited%20coat%20closet%20sits%20on%20the%20right%2C%20but%20the%20left%20side%20was%20a%20blank%20canvas%20for%20Degreff%20to%20decorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20a%20bench%20seating%20with%20a%20little%20open%20shelf%2C%20something%20that%20I%20could%20restyle%20seasonally%2C%20and%20a%20spot%20to%20hang%20extra%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20did%20the%20work%20on%20the%20corner%20herself%2C%20adding%20paneling%20to%20the%20wall%20behind%20and%20next%20to%20the%20bench%20for%20some%20texture.%20A%20wooden%20shelf%20floated%20above%20the%20bench%2C%20and%20Degreff%20added%20hooks%20to%20the%20wall%20for%20jackets%20and%20purses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDegreff%20said%20the%20mudroom%20is%20already%20making%20her%20home%20more%20functional.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20grabs%20a%20purse%20in%20the%20entryway%20of%20her%20home%2C%20which%20is%20painted%20green.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686ec16385e81483682db0b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESteffy%20Degreff%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20nice%2C%26quot%3B%20Degreff%20said%20of%20having%20a%20mudroom.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20the%20first%20winter%20that%20we%20walked%20into%20having%20a%20mudroom%2C%20and%20it's%20just%20so%20much%20easier%20having%20a%20place%20to%20put%20the%20kids'%20sports%20bags%20and%20hang%20up%20our%20coats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20work%2C%20I%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20random%20props%20that%20I%20get%2C%20and%20I%20have%20a%20closet%20space%20there%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20sitting%20by%20the%20front%20door%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20living%20room.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20archway%20also%20improved%20the%20home's%20curb%20appeal%2C%20as%20Degreff's%20neighbors%20can%20attest.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20home%20with%20a%20yellow%20door%20and%20a%20brick%20arch%20in%20the%20front.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686ec11785e81483682db0a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESteffy%20Degreff%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20arch%20drastically%20changed%20the%20house's%20appearance%2C%20but%20Degreff%20said%20all%20the%20work%20they%20did%20on%20the%20exterior%20in%202024%20improved%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-making-outside-of-home-look-worse-curb-appeal-designers-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecurb%20appeal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20adding%20sod%2C%20we%20added%20a%20fence%2C%20we%20added%20landscaping%2C%20so%20the%20arch%20is%20just%20like%20a%20piece%20of%20other%20things%20that%20definitely%20made%20the%20house%20more%20attractive%20from%20the%20outside%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDegreff%20said%20people%20who%20live%20in%20her%20community%20noticed%20the%20upgrades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20amount%20of%20neighbors%20that%20are%20excited%20about%20it%20has%20also%20been%20really%20cute%2C%26quot%3B%20Degreff%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20at%20least%20one%20neighbor%20every%20day%2C%20and%20it's%20been%20a%20year%2C%20that's%20like%2C%20'Your%20house%20came%20out%20so%20great.%20I%20love%20how%20it%20looks.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20feels%20like%20the%20exterior%20finally%20matches%20the%20interior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20realized%20that%20it%20was%20cute%20inside%20because%20it%20had%20sad%20grass%20and%20it%20was%20just%20so%20dumpy%20outside%2C%20and%20now%20I%20feel%20like%20people%20get%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20first%20did%20the%20renovation%2C%20people%20asked%20me%20when%20I%20moved%20in%20and%20welcomed%20me%20to%20the%20neighborhood%20because%20they%20thought%20I%20had%20just%20bought%20the%20house%20and%20started%20to%20fix%20it%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EShe%20also%20has%20fun%20changing%20up%20her%20doorway%20seasonally.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20the%20staircase%20of%20her%20house%20on%20a%20snowy%20day.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687015eaf748d8c055f56396%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESteffy%20Degreff%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDegreff%20has%20been%20switching%20up%20the%20decor%20out%20front%20to%20match%20the%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDecorating%20it%20every%20season%20has%20been%20so%20fun%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20put%20leaves%20around%20the%20arch%20for%20fall%20last%20year%2C%20and%20then%20I%20did%20garlands%20and%20lights%20for%20Christmas%2C%20and%20it's%20just%20fun%20and%20festive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20BI%20that%20she's%20also%20%26quot%3Bconstantly%26quot%3B%20repainting%20the%20front%20door.%20Degreff%20knows%20repainting%20it%20so%20often%20might%20lead%20to%20wear%20and%20tear%20long-term%2C%20but%20she%20considers%20it%20a%20work%20expense%20because%20so%20much%20of%20her%20content%20revolves%20around%20her%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20sand%20it%20in%20between%2C%20but%20it%20does%20get%20thick.%20It's%20definitely%20a%20casualty%2C%20and%20I%20look%20at%20it%20as%20a%20business%20expense%20at%20this%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWorst%20case%20scenario%2C%20I%20will%2C%20in%20five%20years%2C%20get%20a%20different%20door%20and%20start%20from%20scratch.%20There's%20nothing%20saying%20the%20door%20has%20to%20be%20forever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHaving%20a%20clear%20vision%20helped%20Degreff%