he%20apprehension%20that%20had%20been%20building.%20A%20stranger%20from%20another%20country%20would%20soon%20be%20staying%20in%20my%20apartment.%20Was%20this%20a%20good%20idea%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222996%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Christmas%20tree%20during%20the%20holidays%20in%202003.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687ea41685e81483682e6551%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222247%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20first%2C%20there%20were%20a%20few%20cultural%20differences%20and%20misunderstandings.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Inna%20Tysoe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b4cb6440-d50a-45c0-8443-213bb49db83c%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20a%20bit%20awkward%20at%20first%2C%20but%20we%20got%20through%20it%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20finally%20met%2C%20we%20discovered%20a%20few%20cultural%20differences.%20Though%20English%20people%20generally%20don't%20tend%20to%20have%20a%20flair%20for%20the%20dramatic%2C%20picking%20up%20stakes%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafter-major-break-up-move-new-city-heal-heartbreak-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoming%20to%20a%20new%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20just%20to%20meet%20someone%20you've%20been%20chatting%20with%20online%20is%20pretty%20bold.%20So%2C%20Adrian%20tried%20to%20compensate%20during%20our%20first%20visit%20by%20making%20his%20surroundings%20a%20bit%20more%20English.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20his%20first%20night%20in%20the%20US%2C%20we%20had%20pizza.%20I%20opened%20the%20box%20and%20took%20a%20slice.%20He%20sat%20staring%20at%20it.%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20have%20a%20knife%20and%20fork%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20inquired.%20I%20assured%20him%20I%20did.%20%26quot%3BCan%20I%20have%20them%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20gaped%2C%20and%20watched%20with%20amusement%20a