y%20relationships%20that%20are%20deeply%20meaningful.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%20are%20the%20five%20top%20things%20every%20stepparent%20should%20avoid%2C%20and%20what%20to%20do%20instead.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c8d838e-99ef-43d4-9cf8-953e93a89f31%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaving%20expectations%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Binstant%20family%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20easy%20to%20get%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20societal%20pressure%20to%20create%20a%20real%20family%20before%20the%20relationships%20are%20fully%20ready%20and%20able%20to%20support%20that.%20Many%20stepparents%20come%20in%20%26quot%3Blove%20blind%26quot%3B%20and%20assume%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20family%20will%20meet%20them%20with%20the%20same%20energy.%20The%20hard%20truth%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkate-hudson-blended-family-positive-different-dads-goldie-hawn-russell-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eblended%20families%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20formed%20from%20some%20form%20of%20loss.%20Whether%20it's%20a%20divorce%2C%20death%20of%20a%20parent%2C%20or%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20family%20unit%20from%20the%20start%2C%20there%20is%20grief%20involved.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20you%20expect%20instant%20connection%20without%20allowing%20space%20for%20those%20complex%20emotions%20to%20exist%2C%20you%20set%20yourself%20up%20for%20disappointment.%20Relationships%20in%20blended%20families%20are%20slow%20to%20develop.%20They%20are%20often%20one%20step%20forward%2C%20two%20steps%20back.%20The%20goal%20should%20be%20allowing%20them%20to%20evolve%20naturally%20and%20on%20their%20own%20unique%20timeline.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295837ae8-1e72-42d7-942f-748001e5f46e%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20overly%20involved%20in%20your%20partner's%20coparenting%20relationship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cs