energetic%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20theory%20is%20that%20even%20if%20you%20use%20a%20growth%20hormone%20stimulating%20peptide%2C%20your%20body's%20only%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20make%20so%20much%20growth%20hormone%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Sajad%20Zalzala%2C%20a%20longevity%20physician%20and%20one%20of%20the%20cofounders%20of%20AgelessRx%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BKind%20of%20like%20a%20check%20valve%20already%20in%20place.%20Again%2C%20that's%20the%20%3Cem%3Etheory%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220bbc0897-6fbd-443a-81f4-5cbd5c70d7e2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20peptides%20gym%20bros%20take%20to%20get%20chiseled%20muscles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hugh%20Jackman%20as%20Logan%2FWolverine%20in%20%26quot%3BDeadpool%20%26amp%3B%20Wolverine.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66aa8f25aab37011780c2deb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHugh%20Jackman%20as%20Logan%2FWolverine%20in%20%26quot%3BDeadpool%20%26amp%3B%20Wolverine.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EJay%20Maidment%2F20th%20Century%20Studios%20and%20Marvel%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20darling%20peptide%20of%20gym%20bros%20and%20longevity%20fiends%20alike%20is%20a%20substance%20called%20%3Cstrong%3EBPC-157%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20It's%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BWolverine%26quot%3B%20shot%20for%20its%20perceived%20ability%20to%20heal%20you%20up%20and%20regenerate%20your%20body%20real%20fast%20like%20the%20Marvel%20character%2C%20Logan%2C%20after%20a%20big%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EB-P-C%20stands%20for%20%26quot%3Bbody%20protection%20compound.%26quot%3B%20BPC-157%20was%20first%20derived%20from%20stomach%20juices.%20It's%20being%20investigated%20to%20treat%20inflammatory%20bowel%20diseases%2C%20including%20Crohn's%20and%20ulcerative%20colitis.%20But%20the%20reason%20that%20athletes%20like%20it%20is%20because%20it's%20thought%20to%20reduce%20inflammation%20and%20improve%20blood%20flow%20%E2%80%94%20and%20perhaps%20do%20even%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20other%20super%20popular%20peptides%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETesamorelin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20an%20injectable%20peptide%2C%20is%20prescribed%20to%20HIV%20patients%20to%20reduce%20excess%20belly%20fat.%20%3Cstrong%3ESermorelin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20supposed%20to%20help%20with%20sleep%20and%20recovery.%20%3Cstrong%3ECJC-1295%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebinds%20to%20growth%20hormone%20receptors%20in%20the%20body%2C%20and%20people%20often%20take%20it%20alongside%20%3Cstrong%3Eimpamorelin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20stimulates%20the%20hypothalamus.%20The%20two%20in%20tandem%20are%20said%20to%20deliver%20better%20muscle%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Reddit%20and%20YouTube%20people%20share%20how%20they%20%26quot%3Bstack%26quot%3B%20different%20peptides%20like%20this%2C%20taking%20multiple%20different%20kinds%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20boosting%20the%20effects%20of%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a55a724-577d-4a2c-a08b-58a29f86e76d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20snag%3A%20The%20FDA%20is%20making%20peptides%20harder%20to%20access%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227952%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22peptide%20vial%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688406d63d5881a51c1e0e82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20can%20be%20near%20impossible%20to%20know%20exactly%20what%20you're%20getting%3Cp%3ELu%20ShaoJi%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPeptide%20fans%20get%20their%20shots%20at%20clinics%20and%20med%20spas%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20for%20less%20money%2C%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasingly%2C%20people%20are%20ordering%20peptides%20that%20are%20labeled%20%26quot%3Bfor%20research%20only%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20they%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20used%20by%20lab%20workers%20for%20experimentation%2C%20and%20were%20never%20meant%20to%20be%20put%20into%20human%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20partly%20because%20the%20FDA%20crackdown%20on%20peptides%20has%20intensified%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20just%20as%20pharmaceutical%20compounding%20(a%20sort%20of%20acceptable%20way%20to%20get%20knock%20off%20medications)%20has%20surged%20in%20popularity%2C%20with%20people%20seeking%20cheaper%20versions%20of%20GLP-1%20drugs%20like%20Ozempic%20and%20Mounjaro.%20At%20the%20beginning%20of%202022%2C%20the%20FDA%20had%20a%20list%20of%20four%20peptides%20that%20they%20said%20%26quot%3Bmay%20present%20significant%20safety%20risks%26quot%3B%20and%20should%20not%20be%20compounded.%20By%20the%20end%20of%202023%2C%20there%20were%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComite%20thinks%20the%20FDA%20crackdown%20is%20a%20shame.%20She%20is%20finding%20it%20harder%20and%20harder%20to%20source%20compounded%20liquid%20BPC-157.%20She%20often%20uses%20a%20patch%20form%20of%20BPC-157%20on%20herself%2C%20placing%20it%20over%20sore%20areas%20or%20injuries.%20Recently%2C%20she%20tore%20a%20calf%20muscle%2C%20so%20she's%20been%20using%20it%20there%2C%20but%20she%20also%20just%20likes%20how%20taking%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20it%20keeps%20her%20active%20and%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20use%20it%20almost%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20amazing%20for%20joints%20and%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20at%20a%20very%20tiny%20dose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZalzala%2C%20who%20doesn't%20usually%20prescribe%20peptides%2C%20ordered%20some%20topical%20BPC-157%20recently%20when%20his%20wife%20had%20a%20knee%20injury.%20%26quot%3BMy%20wife%20says%20it%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20though%20he%20cautioned%20that%20it's%20hard%20to%20really%20know%20if%20that's%20true%20without%20more%20proper%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bracken%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688407c43d5881a51c1e0e8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223309%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVF%20Corporation%20CEO%20Bracken%20Darrell%20(pictured%20in%20February%202024)%20recently%20used%20BPC-157%20on%20a%20knee%20injury.%3Cp%3ETommaso%20Boddi%2FWWD%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBracken%20Darrell%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20VF%20Corporation%20and%20one%20of%20Comite's%20patients%2C%20is%20also%20a%20BPC-157%20convert.%20A%20self-proclaimed%20%26quot%3Bbasketball%20nut%2C%26quot%3B%20he's%20on%20the%20court%20about%20three%20days%20a%20week.%20On%20the%20days%20when%20he%20doesn't%20pick%20up%20a%20ball%2C%20he's%20out%20cross-training%20on%20a%20bike%20or%20lifting%20weights.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20he%20tore%20his%20meniscus%20about%20four%20months%20ago%2C%20he%20was%20worried.%20Under%20Comite's%20supervision%2C%20he%20started%20taking%20liquid%20BPC-157%20about%20three%20to%20four%20times%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20BI%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bweird%26quot%3B%20at%20first%2C%20learning%20to%20inject%20the%20needle%20into%20an%20area%20of%20skin%20near%20his%20knee.%20But%2C%20pretty%20soon%2C%20it%20was%20just%20part%20of%20his%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20it%20helped%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20it's%20hard%20to%20know%20for%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20people%20with%20a%20severely%20torn%20meniscus%20who%20don't%20ever%20play%20basketball%20again%2C%20and%20I'm%20back%20%E2%80%94%20I%20certainly%20wouldn't%20conclude%20that's%20because%20I'm%20taking%20BPC-157%2C%20but%20at%20a%20minimum%20it%20didn't%20hurt.%20And%20it%20sure%20seems%20like%20it%20helps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227187d431-c84c-4062-b608-e8c260fab918%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EProceed%20with%20caution%2C%20doctors%20say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22man%20lifting%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6884084c85e81483682ebca3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWorking%20with%20peptides%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20like%20Lowe's%20or%20Home%20Depot%20where%20you%20can%20get%20stuff%20and%20you%20can%20fix%20the%20plumbing%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Comite%20said.%3Cp%3EZorica%20Nastasic%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20longevity%20doctors%20who%20prescribe%20and%20use%20peptides%20regularly%20agree%20that%20some%20folks%20are%20overdoing%20it%2C%20and%20that%20could%20be%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProceed%20with%20caution%2C%20because%20you%20have%20to%20know%20the%20source%20and%20you%20have%20to%20know%20it's%20active%2C%26quot%3B%20Comite%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20Lowe's%20or%20Home%20Depot%20where%20you%20can%20get%20stuff%20and%20you%20can%20fix%20the%20plumbing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20reality%2C%20the%20evidence%20for%20peptides%20is%20still%20murky.%20There%20are%20no%20big%2C%20randomized%20clinical%20trials%20like%20what%20we%20have%20for%20prescription%20drugs%20or%20vaccines.%20The%20current%20hype%20is%20based%20on%20anecdotal%20evidence%2C%20a%20few%20small%20human%20studies%20from%20decades%20ago%2C%20and%20rodent%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20wanna%20take%20the%20peptides%20because%20they're%20not%20from%20big%20pharma%2C%20they're%20not%20mainstream%20medicine%2C%20they%20gotta%20be%20better%20than%20those%20cockamamie%20doctors%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forgan-age-test-what-proteomics-can-reveal-about-health-longevity-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDr.%20Eric%20Topol%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20cardiologist%20and%20longevity%20expert%2C%20said%20recently%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkristen-bell-dax-shepard-therapy-helps-marriage-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDax%20Shepard%3C%2Fa%3E%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BWhere's%20the%20data%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20people%20who%20are%20using%20peptides%2C%20experts%20shared%20two%20pieces%20of%20advice%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComite%20urges%20patients%20to%20start%20slow.%20A%20common%20mistake%20people%20who%20are%20dosing%20themselves%20make%20is%20thinking%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20a%20little%20bit%20is%20good%2C%20then%20a%20lot%20must%20be%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20That's%20not%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20mega%20doses%20of%20tesmorelin%20along%20with%20testosterone%20causes%20your%20organs%20to%20overgrow%2C%26quot%3B%20Comite%20said.%20Sometimes%20she'll%20see%20a%20toned%20gymgoer%20with%20a%20potbelly%2C%20and%20wonder%20whether%20that's%20due%20to%20an%20enlarged%20liver%20or%20spleen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDarrell%20recommends%20testing%20your%20peptides%20with%20an%20independent%20lab%20so%20you%20know%20what%20you're%20getting%20is%20both%20real%20and%20uncontaminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZalzala%20says%20his%20company%20started%20thinking%20about%20offering%20peptides%20a%20few%20years%20back%2C%20due%20to%20consumer%20demand%2C%20but%20they%20haven't%20yet.%20There%20are%20just%20so%20many%20peptides%20out%20there%2C%20and%20it's%20hard%20to%20tell%20which%20might%20be%20the%20very%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsimple-longevity-tricks-to-improve-diet-routine-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch-backed%20ways%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20your%20longevity%20and%20fitness%20are%20still%20the%20simplest%20anyway%3A%20eat%20decent%20amounts%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprotein-and-high-fiber-breakfast-key-to-losing-weight-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiber%20and%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%20regularly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmuscle-building-potential-gains-progress-monthly-trainer-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D