Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20harm%20in%20using%20AI%20or%20templates%2C%20but%20the%20customization%20is%20not%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20hurting%20your%20chances%20by%20sounding%20like%20everyone%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20tools%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20introduce%20factual%20errors%20in%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%2C%20which%20are%20often%20apparent%20to%20recruiters%20because%20dates%2C%20numbers%2C%20and%20other%20details%20are%20inconsistent%20with%20what%20is%20on%20a%20candidate's%20LinkedIn%20profile%20or%20what%20the%20person%20says%20during%20the%20interview%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20a%20real%20fine-tooth%20comb%20to%20what%20AI%20produces%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Desiree%20Goldey%2C%20a%20recruiter%20in%20Austin%2C%20Texas%2C%20who%20reviews%20an%20average%20of%20500%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20a%20week%20and%20estimates%20that%20about%20half%20are%20written%20with%20AI%20to%20the%20point%20that%20it's%20noticeable.%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20it%20saves%20you%20time%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20go%20back%20and%20look%20at%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20written%20by%20AI%20tend%20to%20come%20across%20as%20soulless%2C%20she%20added.%20The%20human%20element%20is%20just%20missing%20and%20that's%20a%20turn-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20portraying%20yourself%20with%20any%20authenticity%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldey%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20become%20this%20robot%20and%20nobody%20is%20going%20to%20hire%20a%20robot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227260ce35-64d4-41bd-a2f1-a53976081f2d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20shows%20up%20in%20interviews%2C%20too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20candidates%20are%20also%20sneaking%20a%20peek%20at%20AI%20apps%20on%20their%20phones%20while%20interviewing%20with%20recruiters%20over%20video%20apps%20such%20as%20Zoom.%20Recruiters%20say%20these%20individuals%20repeat%20the%20questions%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethey've%20been%20asked%20out%20loud%2C%20then%20sneak%20glances%20to%20the%20side%20of%20the%20screen%20at%20whatever%20AI%20program%20they're%20using%20so%20they%20can%20read%20the%20results%20it%20spits%20out.%20They%20also%20usually%20take%20a%20brief%20pause%20before%20answering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldey%20said%20it's%20fine%20to%20practice%20interviewing%20with%20AI%2C%20but%20when%20it's%20time%20to%20go%20on%20camera%2C%20she%20expects%20candidates%20to%20look%20at%20her%20the%20whole%20time%20%E2%80%94%20not%20their%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20use%20AI%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20me%20is%20a%20no%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20worst%20thing%20you%20could%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBonnie%20Dilber%2C%20a%20senior%20talent-acquisition%20manager%20for%20a%20fully%20remote%20software%20company%2C%20said%20she's%20seen%20such%20behavior%20rising%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20She%20recalled%20an%20instance%20in%20which%20a%20candidate%20went%20even%20further%20by%20using%20an%20AI%20filter%20to%20impose%20their%20face%20on%20another%20person's%20body.%20The%20other%20individual%20%E2%80%94%20the%20one%20who%20could%20only%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20neck%20down%20%E2%80%94%20answered%20the%20recruiter's%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20see%20the%20filter%20glitch%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDilber%20suspects%20people%20are%20going%20to%20such%20lengths%20because%20they%20lack%20confidence%20in%20their%20interviewing%20skills%20and%20believe%20AI%20will%20give%20them%20an%20edge.%20Or%2C%20she%20said%20they%20could%20be%20engaging%20in%20fraudulent%20activity%2C%20such%20as%20trying%20to%20understand%20the%20interview%20process%20so%20they%20can%20sell%20the%20information%20they%20glean%20to%20job%20seekers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20other%20recruiters%20on%20her%20team%20use%20an%20AI%20platform%20that%20records%20interviews%20for%20generating%20transcripts%20and%20summarizing%20what's%20discussed.%20If%20they%20sense%20something%20is%20fishy%2C%20they'll%20review%20the%20footage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecording%20the%20interviews%20for%20us%20is%20a%20huge%20way%20that%20we%20can%20catch%20these%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Dilber%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20imagine%20a%20future%20in%20which%20maybe%20to%20begin%20an%20interview%2C%20you%20have%20to%20scan%20an%20ID.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20job-search%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20the%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asneedleman%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Esneedleman%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E'%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Es%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecruiters-job-search-resume-interview-ai-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753522621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883e55d3d5881a51c1e0bff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecruiters-job-search-resume-interview-ai-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recruiters%20say%20they're%20getting%20stuck%20with%20piles%20of%20robotic-sounding%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20and%20applicants%20who%20are%20like