eds%20of%20couples.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20works%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-10-most-expensive-cities-for-ultra-rich-in-2025-2025-7%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eultra-high%20net%20worth%3C%2Fa%3E%20individuals%2C%20charging%20rates%20from%20%24150%2C000%20to%20%24500%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPart%20of%20the%20job%2C%20she%20says%2C%20is%20pushing%20back%20when%20what%20a%20client%20wants%20isn't%20what%20they%20need.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jennifer%20Donnelly%2C%20a%20Dallas-based%20matchmaker%20for%20wealthy%20individuals.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20with%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20influential%20people%20to%20help%20them%20find%20that%20compatible%20partner.%20My%20sorority%20sister%20is%20married%20through%20me%2C%20and%20the%20person%20who%20lived%20across%20the%20street%20from%20me%20when%20I%20was%20eight%20years%20old%20is%20married%20through%20me.%20It's%20such%20a%20rewarding%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20college%2C%20I%20worked%20for%20a%20company%20that%20matched%20people%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-nightmare-tea-whisper-network-apps-save-us-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edating%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20a%20really%20high%20volume%20of%20people%2C%20like%20thousands%2C%20at%20a%20lower%20price%20point%2C%20and%20we%20were%20only%20matching%20people%20inside%20that%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20client%2C%20get%20to%20know%20them%2C%20and%20search%20all%20over%20for%20the%20right%20fit.%20So%20I%20said%2C%20if%20I%20do%20this%20again%2C%20it%20should%20be%20for%20fewer%20clients%20at%20a%20higher%20price%20point%20to%20deliver%20exceptional%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20matchmaking%20specific