ee.%20My%20clients%20are%20understandably%20very%20private%2C%20so%20I%20have%20to%20get%20them%20comfortable%20being%20vulnerable%20because%20I%20can%20only%20be%20as%20good%20as%20they%20allow%20me%20to%20be.%20I'll%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20effective%20the%20more%20information%20I%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20wealthy%20men%20are%20used%20to%20people%20telling%20them%20what%20they%20want%20to%20hear.%20I%20don't%20do%20that.%20This%20is%20about%20being%20effective%20and%20having%20a%20successful%20outcome.%20And%20oftentimes%20that%20requires%20a%20level%20of%20honesty%20that%20somebody%20hasn't%20presented%20to%20them%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20what%20people%20want%20and%20what%20they%20need%20is%20different.%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20I%20want%20her%20to%20have%20an%20incredible%20career%2C%20to%20be%20a%20great%20mom%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20travel%20at%20a%20moment's%20notice%20because%20I've%20got%20a%20plane.%26quot%3B%20And%20how%20can%20all%20of%20those%20things%20fit%3F%20Let's%20talk%20about%20what%20really%20matters%20in%20the%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20start%2C%20I%20explain%20it%20might%20take%20up%20to%20six%20weeks.%20But%20if%20we're%20at%20six%20weeks%2C%20and%20I%20have%20not%20found%20the%20person%2C%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20just%20put%20somebody%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20I'll%20just%20keep%20looking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20create%20strategy%20plans%20for%20each%20client.%20We%20create%20a%20profile%20of%20what%20we%20envision%20for%20that%20client%2C%20and%20then%20we'll%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BOkay%2C%20how%20are%20we%20going%20to%20find%20people%20like%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20then%20we'll%20start%20working%20through%20our%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20thing%20is%20we're%20incredibly%20well-connected.%20It%20would%20be%20highly%20unusual%20if%20there%20was%20a%20candidate%20we%20wanted%20that%20I%20couldn't%20get%20through%20somebody%20I%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20that%20they%20truly%20want%20a%20relationship.%20I%20always%20ask%20candidates%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20dating%20anybody%3F%20Does%20anybody%20think%20they're%20dating%20you%3F%20You%20could%20end%20up%20married%3B%20are%20you%20ready%20for%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20There's%20other%20matchmakers%20that%20can%20create%20dates.%20I'm%20really%20trying%20to%20create%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'll%20conduct%20sometimes%20over%20100%20interviews%20before%20a%20client%20goes%20on%20one%20date.%20We%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20this%20isn't%20a%20waste%20of%20time%20for%20the%20client%20or%20the%20candidate%3B%20we%20would%20like%20to%20think%20we're%20matching%20for%20both%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20dates%20go%2C%20it%20can%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20dinner%20to%20something%20much%20more%20elaborate.%20The%20client%20can%20decide%20if%20they'd%20like%20to%20help%20plan%20it%2C%20or%20leave%20it%20to%20us%20or%20have%20their%20assistants%20plan%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20attending%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-weddings-summer-calendar-jeff-bezos-alex-soros-eve-jobs-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweddings%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20couples%20I've%20matched.%20That's%20the%20prize%20for%20me.%20It's%20like%2C%20OK%2C%20I%20did%20it%2C%20this%20is%20why%20I'm%20in%20this%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20oftentimes%20the%20couple%20will%20tell%20me%20at%20their%20wedding%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20please%20don't%20mention%20you're%20a%20matchmaker.%20Just%20say%20you're%20a%20'consultant.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatchmaker-uber-wealthy-price-interviews-jennifer-donnelly-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753522261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688399243d5881a51c1dff5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatchmaker