e%20the%20world%20of%20crypto%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julia%20Burlingham%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883ba1a3d5881a51c1e0539%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulia%20Burlingham%20is%20the%20owner%20of%20Professional%20Crypto%20Recovery%2C%20a%20company%20that%20helps%20people%20recover%20their%20lost%20crypto.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Burlingham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229eb98392-c10b-42b0-854e-7a3aa55064ca%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20crypto%20storage%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20main%20ways%20of%20holding%20crypto%3A%20on%20an%20exchange%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoinbase-hack-how-to-protect-crypto-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECoinbase%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20through%20self-custody%20using%20your%20own%20crypto%20wallet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20self-custody%20provides%20more%20control%20and%20privacy%2C%20the%20responsibility%20of%20securing%20the%20wallet%20lies%20in%20%E2%80%94%20as%20the%20name%20implies%20%E2%80%94%20yourself.%20Setting%20up%20a%20self-custody%20wallet%20generates%20a%20seed%20phrase%20of%2012%20or%2024%20random%20words%20that%20encodes%20your%20private%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20often%20write%20the%20seed%20phrase%20down%20with%20pen%20and%20paper%2C%20according%20to%20Jess%20Houlgrave%2C%20CEO%20at%20the%20digital%20asset%20startup%20Reown.%20Issues%20arise%20when%20that%20slip%20of%20paper%20isn't%20stored%20securely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20you're%20in%20the%20self-custodial%20realm%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20store%20and%20recover%20your%20seed%20phrase%20in%20order%20to%20be%20able%20to%20use%20the%20assets%2C%26quot%3B%20Houlgrave%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20also%20seen%20people%20store%20their%20passkeys%20on%20Google%20Drive%20or%20password%20managers%2C%20which%20Houlgrave%20doesn't%20recommend%2C%20as%20those%20methods%20are%20susceptible%20to%20being%20hacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Houlgrave%20and%20Burlingham%20mentioned%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-la-fire-damage-cost-estimate-who-pays-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELA%20wildfires%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%20resulted%20in%20many%20people%20losing%20their%20seed%20phrases%20when%20their%20homes%20burned%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Reuters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fwallet-recovery-firms-buzz-locked-out-crypto-investors-panic-bitcoin-boom-2024-05-15%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFuture%2520of%2520Money-%2CWallet%2520recovery%2520firms%2520buzz%2520as%2520locked%252Dout%2Cinvestors%2520panic%2520in%2520bitcoin%2520boom%3DMay%252015%2520(Reuters)%2520%252D%2520The%2Cregain%2520access%2520to%2520their%2520accounts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20some%20wallet%20recovery%20services%20saw%20requests%20for%20their%20services%20more%20than%20triple%20when%20bitcoin%20rose%20to%20%2470%2C000.%20Now%2C%20with%20bitcoin%20prices%20firmly%20in%20six-figure%20territory%2C%20the%20stakes%20are%20even%20higher.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220b1d9cd8-4dcb-4e38-99f2-47ecd60e2ab7%5C%22%3EA%20day%20in%20the%20life%20of%20a%20crypto%20locksmith%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBurlingham%20helps%20people%20with%20issues%20such%20as%20forgotten%20passwords%2C%20partial%20seed%20phrases%2C%20corrupted%20wallet%20files%2C%20or%20old%20wallets%20that%20no%20longer%20sync%20with%20the%20blockchains.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20clients%20range%20from%20original%20bitcoin%20investors%20who%20bought%20over%20a%20decade%20ago%20to%20people%20who%20just%20set%20up%20their%20accounts%20recently%20and%20suddenly%20lost%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDepending%20on%20the%20wallet%2C%20sometimes%20you%20can%20brute%20force%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Burlingham%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20if%20you%20remember%20fragments%20of%20a%20password%20or%20seed%20phrase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20ask%20for%20password%20clues%20and%20how%20they%20typically%20make%20their%20passwords%2C%26quot%3B%20Burlingham%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20specialized%20supercomputers%20with%20high%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-tenets-ai-projects-prioritize-gpus-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGPU%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20CPU%20power%2C%20Burlingham%20runs%20password%20recovery%20tools%20that%20test%20millions%20of%20combinations.%20Because%20wallets%20and%20private%20keys%20are%20highly%20sensitive%2C%20she%20runs%20them%20on%20air-gapped%20computers%2C%20or%20machines%20that%20aren't%20connected%20to%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurlingham%20also%20helps%20those%20who%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fzelle-scams%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escammed%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20their%20crypto%2C%20a%20growing%20problem.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Chainalysis%2C%20more%20than%20%242%20billion%20was%20stolen%20from%20cryptocurrency%20services%20already%20in%202025%2C%20surpassing%20the%20total%20for%20all%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recovery%20process%20can%20take%20months.%20One%20case%20that%20Burlingham%20started%20in%20November%20of%20last%20year%20took%20until%20this%20April%20to%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecovering%20crypto%20is%20also%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-stablecoins-how-to-invest-trump-genius-act-btc-eth-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenergy%20intensive%3C%2Fa%3E%20endeavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20Burlingham%20said%20of%20her%20electricity%20bill.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20have%20cooling%20systems%20because%20these%20machines%20produce%20a%20lot%20of%20heat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8cb8785-1bd8-4dc3-bf0b-3cc17e159d93%5C%22%3ELost%20crypto%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20sometimes%2C%20nothing%20can%20be%20done%20to%20recover%20the%20crypto.%20According%20to%20crypto%20wallet%20provider%20Ledger%2C%20it's%20estimated%20that%20between%20two%20and%20four%20million%20bitcoins%20are%20permanently%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-hard-drive-750-million-dump-landfill-site-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJames%20Howell%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20infamous%20example%20of%20this%20unlucky%20outcome%20%E2%80%94%20the%20IT%20worker%20accidentally%20threw%20away%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-howells-threw-away-bitcoin-dump-masterplan-get-back-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20hard%20drive%3C%2Fa%3E%20containing%208%2C000%20bitcoins%20back%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20crypto%2C%20an%20ounce%20of%20prevention%20is%20worth%20a%20pound%20%E2%80%94%20or%20several%20%E2%80%94%20of%20cure.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMake%20multiple%20copies%20of%20your%20seed%20phrase%20and%20putting%20them%20into%20secure%20physical%20locations%2C%20such%20as%20a%20locked%20safe%20or%20bank%20vault%2C%20Burlingham%20recommends.%20And%20it%20may%20sound%20simple%2C%20but%20avoiding%20phishing%20links%20and%20keeping%20your%20seed%20phrase%20private%20are%20steps%20that%20many%20people%20still%20overlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-lost-wallet-recovery-forgot-password-crypto-scam-rally-btc-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753522201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68716cc93d5881a51c1d36f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-lost-wallet-recovery-forgot-password-crypto-scam-rally-btc-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bitcoin%20is%20surg