about%20AI%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-equity-partners-problem-pwc-deloitte-ey-kpmg-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20consulting%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20as%20the%20class%20had%20already%20started%2C%20I%20slipped%20in%20quietly%20and%20took%20a%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20KPMG%20helps%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20companies%20figure%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-ai-boss-david-rowlands-artificial-intelligence-strategy-big-four-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20use%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20curious%20to%20see%20how%20the%20consulting%20giant%20was%20teaching%20its%20own%20employees%20to%20use%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20biggest%20takeaway%3F%20Upskilling%20for%20the%20AI%20era%20can%20be%20surprisingly%20basic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f28f081-cc66-4bcb-92f6-b61e81dca22b%5C%22%3EThe%20five%20ways%20of%20asking%20AI%20a%20question%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20large%20screens%20%E2%80%94%20two%20on%20each%20wall%E2%80%94%20hung%20down%20from%20the%20ceiling%20in%20the%20classroom%2C%20and%20the%2090%20interns%20sat%20around%20circular%20tables%20in%20groups%20of%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESherry%20Magee%2C%20a%20senior%20director%20at%20KPMG%2C%20told%20me%20during%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20property%20that%20the%20space%20was%20designed%20so%20there%20was%20no%20%26quot%3Bfront%20row%20of%20the%20classroom%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20she%20said%20encourages%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20training%20session%20was%20run%20by%20two%20KPMG%20employees.%20They%20opened%20with%20a%20question%20about%20the%20interns'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-consulting-ai-threat-jobs-ey-deloitte-kpmg-pwc-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Euse%20of%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BWho%20just%20generally%20goes%20straight%20to%20it%20and%20just%20starts%20typing%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPretty%20much%20everyone%20in%20the%20room%20raised%20a%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20instructors%20explained%20that%20instead%20of%20chatting%20with%20AI%2C%20there%20were%20five%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-guide-prompt-engineering-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprompting%20techniques%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20could%20use%20to%20adjust%20the%20model's%20response%20to%20get%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%2C%20most%20relevant%2C%20and%20accurate%20output.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20techniques%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EChunking%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20dividing%20a%20large%20prompt%20into%20smaller%2C%20more%20manageable%20requests%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFew-shot%20prompting%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20giving%20the%20AI%20a%20few%20examples%20to%20guide%20its%20response%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIterative%20question%20refinement%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20repeatedly%20rephrasing%20or%20refining%20your%20questions%20to%20lead%20the%20AI%20to%20a%20more%20precise%20response%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EChain%20of%20thought%20prompting%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20asking%20AI%20to%20include%20a%20breakdown%20of%20how%20it%20has%20reached%20an%20answer%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlipped%20interaction%20prompting%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20requesting%20that%20the%20AI%20ask%20you%20questions%20to%20prompt%20new%20thoughts%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20work%20best%20for%20different%20tasks%2C%20the%20instructors%20explained.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bchain%20of%20thought%26quot%3B%20prompt%20can%20be%20useful%20to%20get%20AI%20to%20show%20its%20work.%20This%20%26quot%3Bthinking%20aloud%26quot%3B%20approach%20is%20more%20transparent%20and%20can%20be%20useful%20for%20tax%20professionals%20who%20need%20to%20check%20the%20results%20for%20inaccuracies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFlipped%20interaction%26quot%3B%20prompts%20could%20be%20used%20in%20a%20tax%20setting%20to%20prepare