-img-1_11zon-1753498249-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753498249-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753498249-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753498249-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-476549%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAritra%20cycled%20nearly%201%2C200%20km%20from%20Agartala%20to%20Nepal%20as%20part%20of%20his%20self-designed%20triathlon%20challenge.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20route%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%20From%20scorching%20heat%20to%20mechanical%20failures%20and%20unpredictable%20roads%2C%20he%20had%20to%20stay%20self-reliant%20throughout.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20stretches%20where%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20see%20a%20decent%20eatery%20or%20repair%20shop%20for%20hours.%20But%20somehow%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20lonely.%20I%20was%20doing%20this%20for%20a%20reason.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20reason%2C%20for%20Aritra%2C%20was%20always%20bigger%20than%20just%20a%20personal%20record.%20%E2%80%9CTripura%20is%20never%20in%20the%20conversation%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20mountaineering%20or%20adventure%20sports.%20I%20wanted%20to%20change%20that.%20I%20wanted%20to%20inspire%20young%20people%20from%20the%20Northeast%20and%20show%20that%20even%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20working%20a%20corporate%20job%2C%20you%20can%20dream%20big.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFellow%20cyclist%20and%20friend%20Debabrata%20Majumdar%2C%20who%20accompanied%20Aritra%20on%20part%20of%20the%20expedition%2C%20recalls%20a%20powerful%20moment%20from%20day%20one.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20faced%20with%20high%20ascents%20from%20the%20two%20long%20mountain%20ranges%20of%20Tripura%20%E2%80%93%20Baramura%20and%20Atharamura.%20It%20was%20very%20hot%20and%20humid