ndia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img_11zon-1753409604-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img_11zon-1753409604-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img_11zon-1753409604-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475893%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJharkhand%20set%20up%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Just%20Transition%20Task%20Force%20in%202022%20to%20plan%20coal%20sector%20transformation.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20vision%20document%20outlines%20decade-wise%20roadmaps%20for%20transitioning%20across%2013%20coal-dependent%20districts.%20Chhattisgarh%20rolled%20out%20community%20energy%20initiatives%20(solar%20electrification%20in%20Bastar%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20villages)%20and%20piloted%20hydrogen%20trucking%20for%20cleaner%20mining%20operations%20at%20the%20district%20level.%20While%20these%20efforts%20are%20commendable%2C%20they%20are%20still%20limited%20to%20a%20few%20states.%20Thus%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20anchor%20state%20just%20transition%20plans%20in%20state%20energy%20policies%20and%20mandate%20the%20submission%20of%20%E2%80%98just%20transition%20roadmaps%E2%80%99%20to%20ensure%20binding%20commitments%20and%20alignment%20with%20central%20energy%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Early%20reskilling%20and%20workforce%20planning%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20district-level%20workforce%20mapping%20in%20coal%20regions%2C%20including%20formal%2C%20informal%2C%20and%20dependent%20populations%2C%20should%20be%20conducted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20workforce%20in%20the%20coal%20sector%20is%20not%20affected%20by%20the%20transition.%20The%20targeted%20reskilling%20for%20jobs%20in%20solar%2C%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%2C%20energy%20efficiency%2C%20and%20green%20hydrogen%20should%20be%20initiated%20at%20leas