0one%20thing%20that%20made%20him%20feel%20alive%20and%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20brought%20him%20closer%20to%20his%20dream%20of%20studying%20at%20the%20Berklee%20College%20of%20Music%20in%20the%20United%20States%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20his%20fingers%20moved%20across%20the%20strings%20and%20his%20voice%20wove%20through%20the%20street%20noise%2C%20people%20slowed%20down.%20Some%20paused.%20One%20filmed.%20The%20video%20travelled%20far%2C%20and%20with%20it%2C%20the%20name%20of%2015-year-old%20Debraj%20Bhattacharya.%20But%20behind%20the%20calm%20exterior%20of%20the%20now-viral%20busker%20lies%20a%20story%20shaped%20by%20personal%20loss%2C%20quiet%20grit%2C%20and%20the%20unwavering%20love%20between%20a%20father%20and%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHolding%20on%20to%20music%20after%20loss%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebraj%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20home%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391614%2Fparai-beat-history-caste-barriers-revival%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emusic%20was%20ever-present.%3C%2Fa%3E%20His%20mother%2C%20a%20singer%20herself%2C%20filled%20their%20small%20home%20with%20songs%20%E2%80%94%20until%20cancer%20took%20her%20away.%20Debraj%20was%20young%20when%20she%20passed%2C%20but%20the%20memory%20of%20her%20voice%20and%20love%20for%20music%20stayed%20on.%20It%20became%20a%20lifeline.%20A%20way%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20something%20that%20loss%20had%20almost%20taken%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-23T155712.602-1753266450.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20Debraj%2C%20music%20became%20a%20lifeline%20after%20he%20lost%20his%20mother.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup